  levelNumber: 4
  levelName: Seibal
  location: Peten, Guatemala
  levelDescription: "Once a fading outpost, Seibal was reborn around 830 AD under
    foreign influence, blending Maya and non-Maya styles.\nIts stelae show warriors
    with foreign dress and serpent motifs, marking a crossroads of cultures.\n\nDespite
    this renewal, Seibal\u2019s glory was brief \u2014 by 950 AD, silence claimed
    its plazas again.\nStill, its art tells of transition, resilience, and the final
    sparks of the Classic Maya world.\nBetween river and jungle, Seibal stood \u2014
    last flame before the night."
